    "• Annotated by two reviewers, each utilizing both KEEPER and full charts separately, resulting in 4 times 80 case adjudications.",
    "• Gold standard was two independent reviewers performing chart review using all available structured and unstructured data.",
    "Results were discussed and iterative chart review continued until all disagreements were resolved.",
    "• Same diseases as Test Set 1.",
    "• Balanced sample (half-likely cases and half-likely non-cases) of 20 cases per disease in the Clinformatics® database."
